    <item>
      <title>野村证券聘请 Sudhir Nemali 担任国际财富首席运营官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nomura-hires-sudhir-nemali-international-wealth-chief-operating-officer-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社周五看到的一份内部备忘录显示，日本野村控股已任命苏迪尔·内马利（Sudhir Nemali）为其国际财富管理业务的董事总经理兼首席运营官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nomura-hires-sudhir-nemali-international-wealth-chief-operating-officer-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 03:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融创中国因被提起清算申请而股价、债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sunac-china-shares-plunge-after-liquidation-petition-filed-against-developer-2025-01-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[融创中国股价和债券周五暴跌，此前该房地产开发商被提起清算申请，尽管 2023 年进行了海外债务重组，但投资者对其业务复苏和还款能力的担忧加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sunac-china-shares-plunge-after-liquidation-petition-filed-against-developer-2025-01-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 02:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，美国银行投资银行家的奖金将增加约 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-bonuses-investment-bankers-rise-about-10-source-says-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士向路透社透露，美国银行投资银行家的奖金池可能比去年增加 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-bonuses-investment-bankers-rise-about-10-source-says-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:39:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德寻求将 FDIC 银行监管期限推迟至 3 月</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackrock-seeks-push-fdic-bank-oversight-deadline-march-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据贝莱德周四发给监管机构的一封信（路透社获得该信），贝莱德已要求美国联邦存款保险公司 (FDIC) 将达成协议的最后期限从周五延长至 3 月 31 日，以就该机构如何监管这家大型资产管理公司对 FDIC 监管银行组织的投资达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackrock-seeks-push-fdic-bank-oversight-deadline-march-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街降低环境关注度，贝莱德退出气候组织</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/blackrock-quits-climate-group-wall-streets-latest-environmental-step-back-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的资产管理公司贝莱德周四表示，将退出净零资产管理人倡议组织，这是迫于共和党政客的压力，最新一家退出以环境为重点的投资者组织的华尔街公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/blackrock-quits-climate-group-wall-streets-latest-environmental-step-back-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 19:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼：支持12月降息作为“最后”调整步骤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-bowman-supported-dec-rate-cut-final-recalibration-step-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼周四表示，她支持上个月的降息，认为这是美国央行货币政策重新调整的“最后一步”，通胀风险上升要求未来采取谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-bowman-supported-dec-rate-cut-final-recalibration-step-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储施密德称央行利率“接近”中性水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-schmid-says-central-bank-near-neutral-interest-rate-level-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[堪萨斯城联储行长杰夫·施密德周四表示，美联储不愿再次降息，因为在新的一年里，美联储将面临经济复苏和通胀仍高于 2% 目标的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/feds-schmid-says-central-bank-near-neutral-interest-rate-level-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利 Del Vecchio 家族将 Monte dei Paschi 的持股比例增至 9.8%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/del-vecchio-family-holding-delfin-ups-stake-mps-978-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[文件显示，已故意大利亿万富翁莱昂纳多德尔维基奥 (Leonardo Del Vecchio) 的控股公司已增持了其在获得救助的银行 Monte dei Paschi 的股份，以增强其在意大利银行业预期整合中的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/del-vecchio-family-holding-delfin-ups-stake-mps-978-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BBVA 降低萨瓦德尔竞标的最低接受条件</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bbva-reduces-minimum-acceptance-condition-sabadell-bid-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙对外银行 (BBVA) 周四表示，该银行已对收购萨瓦德尔银行的投标进行了调整，降低了最低接受条件，因为该投标不包括目标规模较小的竞争对手的库存股数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bbva-reduces-minimum-acceptance-condition-sabadell-bid-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 17:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安永调查发现，瑞士银行面临利润率下降困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-banks-struggle-with-lower-margins-ey-survey-finds-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安永（EY）周四表示，由于利率下降，以及瑞信 2023 年破产后信贷需求增加，瑞士银行已下调未来几年的盈利预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-banks-struggle-with-lower-margins-ey-survey-finds-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 15:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不论好坏，全球债券市场动荡都未波及欧元区</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/good-reasons-bad-global-bond-wobble-passes-over-euro-zone-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在英国和美国面临投资者担心债务增长和通胀居高不下的压力之际，欧元区似乎基本逃脱了市场的愤怒——尽管这种平静背后的原因并不全是令人愉快的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/good-reasons-bad-global-bond-wobble-passes-over-euro-zone-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 15:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
